title: Hannah Montana The Movie (2009) [OST] [PBX]
description:
Hannah Montana The Movie OST

This is a rip of the Disney XD website, I then riped and edited it all into mp3!

This is a High Quality recording @ 320Kbps J-Stereo MP3

Originally recorded @ 48000 Sample Rate, 32bit Float Point in WAV Format.


8/10 QA and i dont give it a full 10/10 because 1. Its not a Studio Rip and 2. Its not a CDRip either!!

Please bear in mind 2 or 3 tracks have a error in the recording where it would sound as if it was a CD playing and it had a scratch, this however lasts less then a 1sec and it wont stay stuck on that place as a CD probably would, this occured on the original WAV recording and my computer was acting UP, Sorry For This but i still have hope youll enjoy it as much as i am!



I also tagged the MP3 Files correctly and added the appropriate cover!


Ill be seeding this as much as possible
